# Application — desktop-фасады (как Sample/Desktop.Application)

**Без MediatR.** Use case = `I*AppService` + `*AppService` + DTO + Mapper.

## Два слоя внутри Application

```text
PUBLIC (Presentation видит):
  Contracts/          I*AppService
  DTOs/               Responses, Commands, Queries
  Mappers/            domain/managers → DTO
  Services/           *AppService + application IHostedService

INTERNAL (только Application/Infrastructure):
  BotEngine/
  ├── Loop/           BotLoopService, IBotController
  ├── Install/        BotInstallerService
  ├── Runtime/        BotRuntime, BotModuleRunner
  ├── Modules/        DisconnectModule, …
  ├── Managers/       HeroManager, MapManager, MovementApi, …
  ├── State/          GameMapModel, TrackedHealth, … (impl Core I*Map/IHealth)
  ├── Addresses/      BotAddressRegistry
  └── Statistics/     StatImpl (internal для StatsManager)
  Extensions/         AddApplication()
```

## Фасад

```csharp
// Contracts/IBotStatusAppService.cs
public interface IBotStatusAppService { BotStatusSnapshot Capture(); }

// Services/Bot/BotStatusAppService.cs
public BotStatusSnapshot Capture() =>
    BotStatusSnapshotMapper.Create(...);
```

Scrutor: `*AppService` в `AddAppServices()`.

## Куда класть

| Что | Папка |
|-----|-------|
| Контракт для VM | `Contracts/I{Name}AppService.cs` |
| Response DTO | `DTOs/Responses/{Feature}/` |
| Маппинг → DTO | `Mappers/{Feature}/` |
| Фасад | `Services/{Feature}/*AppService.cs` |
| Tick loop, managers | `BotEngine/` |
| Impl Core `IGameMap` | `BotEngine/State/` |

## Запрещено

- ❌ MediatR
- ❌ `Models/` для UI DTO
- ❌ Корневые `Bot/`, `Managers/`, `Entities/`, `Memory/` (только `BotEngine/`)
- ❌ Presentation → `BotEngine.*` (кроме DI composition root)
